<author>K.J.C. Redemption Songs 7, W.H. Doane</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien lopi hen thil lopi A hih a,
 Khawvel A hehpih a, A Chapa ei pie'i;
 Gitloh khuhna ding in A hinna A pie'i,
 Micheng lut theih na'n Hinna Lampi a hawng.

[V2]
 Lalpa chuh! Pakchau un!
 Lei in A aw za hen;
 Lalpa chuh! Pakchau un!
 Mihingte kipak hen,
 Chapa Isu min in Pa kiengah hungun!
 Lopina pieu in, thil lopi A hih tai.

[V3]
 2. A thih na'n tatna bukim ei siem sak tai,
 A gingcha cheng kienga Pathien in A tiem;
 Migilo pen inle Amah a gin chun,
 Zie hun laitak chun Isu'n A ngaidam hi.

[V4]
 3. Thil lopite ei sinsaka, ei hilh tai,
 A Chapa Isu ziek' I kipahna sa'ng!
 Thiengtho zaw, sangzaw dinga khangto zel di'n,
 Isu I muh tieng maksak na'n dim hitiu.</lyrics>
<title>TO GOD BE THE GLORY!</title>
</song>